import re
	
	#Get data from structure
	strPath = value + "/Sts/Diagnostics/Structure"
	data = system.tag.readBlocking([strPath])[0].value
	generalData = data["General"]

	#Initialise
	arrInstances = []
	filteredMembers = ["Reserved"]
	for bit in generalData:
		if bit not in filteredMembers:
			spacedLabel = re.sub(r'((?<=[a-z])[A-Z]|(?<!\A)[A-Z](?=[a-z]))', r' \1', bit)
			instance = {
			  "instanceStyle": {
			    "classes": ""
			  },
			  "instancePosition": {},
			  "Label": spacedLabel,
			  "ShowLabel": True,
			  "Value": generalData[bit]
			}
			arrInstances.append(instance)
	return arrInstances
